I visited Dr. Bindu Stalekar’s clinic in Panjim for a salicylic acid peel, clean-up, and a calming mask and my skin feels SO much better! 🧖‍♀️💆‍♀️

This treatment targets active pimples, excess oil, and pigmentation and trust me, my skin already feels smoother and more balanced. It takes about 2-3 days to show results so stay calm and see your skin improving 😌🌿

If you’ve been struggling with breakouts or uneven texture, this might just be your skin’s new best friend. 💚
